<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Logout</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#0f1712;
      --card:#243528;
      --accent:#88c273;
      --danger:#d96b6b;
      --radius:14px;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, Arial;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}

    body{
      margin:0;
      min-height:100vh;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0f1712,#16231a);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      color:#f7f5ef;
    }

    .box{
      width:100%;
      max-width:340px;
      background:var(--card);
      padding:22px;
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      text-align:center;
    }

    h3{
      margin-top:0;
    }

    .actions{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:18px;
    }

    button{
      flex:1;
      padding:10px;
      border:none;
      border-radius:10px;
      font-weight:700;
      cursor:pointer;
    }

    .cancel{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      color:#fff;
    }

    .logout{
      background:var(--danger);
      color:#fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="box">
  <h3>Đăng xuất?</h3>
  <p>Bạn có chắc muốn đăng xuất khỏi OwlLoop không?</p>

  <div class="actions">
    <button class="cancel" onclick="location.href='/'">Hủy</button>

    <form method="POST" action="/auth/logout">
      <button class="logout">Đăng xuất</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
